data.description: Looking for a place to call home?  This 3 bedroom/ 2.5 bath residence checks all the boxes. On a waterfront lot in the family-friendly Heather Lakes neighborhood, conveniently located near tennis courts, schools, shopping, and dining, and only minutes to Downtown Tampa. This home features vaulted ceilings, unique architectural details with an open two story floor plan waiting for your personal touches. The 2-car garage offers tons of room for vehicles, hobbies, and storage. The rear doors lead out to the screened-in patio overlooking the enormous lot with lush green lawn and a tranquil lake perfect for a peaceful resting space. The three large bedrooms are positioned to catch plenty of natural light. The huge master suite features a vast walk-in closet, private bathroom with a shower and separate bathtub .  The gigantic Livingroom flows into the formal dining area and the kitchen is fully equipped with an attached 2nd dining area along with a butler's pantry for additional storage. This hidden gem won't last long, so call now to schedule your private tour!
